---
title: Easy As BBQ Prawns & Carrot Tacos with Charred Corn & Sour Cream
description: It’s all hands on deck, this recipe is designed to be cooked by grown-ups and kids together! Welcome to the American South, where the barbecue is famous and plentiful! Try this succulent, tangy prawns to see what all the hype is about. Enjoy with a good dollop of sour cream packed in to warm tacos for a Tex-Mex twist.
